The headphones come equipped with Bluetooth V5.0 for instant wireless connectivity. Apart from the wireless connectivity, one can utilize the AUX cable as well for a wired playback experience. Though we reckon that it will rarely come into use cause of the headphone super powerful 750mAh battery: it provides a humongous playtime of up to 70 hours! Get ready to get enthralled by the pumped up audio and soaring vibe of Rockerz 450 Pro.

This neckband has been designed keeping both style and efficiency in mind. We have paid a lot of attention into fulfilling the promise of durability. Wave your goodbye to those fragile and delicate neckbands because this wonder product right here is flexible, foldable, and easy to store! Our earbuds are never poles apart. The magnetic feature makes them stay put, whether in your pocket or in the front section of your bag. Alpino flex pro is very lightweight compared to other counter products and is feels comfortable around your neck. We ensure we use skin safe material in the making of our products! We believe in making products that are as fashionable as they are efficient. This Bluetooth neckband incorporates the perfect balance of functionality and class. An invisible nano-coating on the band makes it sweat-resistant and easy to clean. Ergonomic sport design with a built-in microphone, this device features buttons to play, pause, and change songs on the go. A battery indicator option comes with the neckband and is operational in specific mobile models. Available in regal matte colors, this neckband features lightning speed Bluetooth connectivity. Furthermore, it is equipped with our A2DP technology that allows you to connect to 2 devices simultaneously. A feature you can hardly find in Bluetooth neckbands. And leaving the best for the last, a 1-2 hour charging time gives you 50 hours of uninterrupted playback! Yes, you heard me right. With a 300mAh battery, it gives you 500 hours of standby time when fully charged so that you use more and charge less!

The headphones come equipped with Bluetooth V5.0 for instant wireless connectivity. Apart from the wireless connectivity, one can utilize the AUX cable as well for a wired playback experience. Though we reckon that it will rarely come into use cause of the headphone super powerful 750mAh battery: it provides a humongous playtime of up to 70 hours! One can control the playback and calls easily via the easily accessible controls and even summon respective smart Voice Assistant. Get ready to get enthralled by the pumped up audio and soaring vibe of Rockerz 450 Pro.
